        <p slot="content">
          Our voice is very much a part of what makes us Red Hat. Use these resources to bring out the Red Hat voice in everything you write.
        </p>
        <rh-cta slot="cta"><a href="https://source.redhat.com/departments/marketing/marketing-content-team/marketing_content_team_wiki/writer_resources_list">Writing resources list</a></rh-cta>
